text: Joseph Weld may refer to: * Captain Joseph Weld (1599-1646), Weld family#Joseph Weld, ancestor of many Boston Welds *Joseph Weld (yachtsman), English yachtsman (1777–1863), brother of Cardinal Thomas Weld *Joseph Weld (MP) (1651–1712), MP for Bury St Edmunds 1709–1712 * Joseph Weld (priest) (?–1781), Archdeacon of Ross * Joseph William Weld (1909–1992), British army officer and landowner
title: Joseph Weld
